query:
INSERT INTO roles (name, description) VALUES
('system_admin', 'Full system access for troubleshooting and advanced configuration'),
('admin', 'Business owner with access to all operations and financial data'),
('sales', 'Lead creation, customer interaction, and follow-ups'),
('appraiser', 'Vehicle inspection and damage assessment'),
('estimator', 'Create and edit estimates, parts ordering'),
('marketing', 'Lead source analytics and campaign tracking'),
('repair_tech', 'Work orders, parts tracking, and repair status updates')
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE description=VALUES(description)
